Welcome to Inform!\n\n \t\t\tWhat is Inform? Inform is an app created to support its users through their experiences with internet gaming. Using the American Psychiatric Association\'s diagnosis criteria for Internet Gaming Disorder, Inform aims to enlighten its users to any potential risks posed by their gaming behaviours through a brief Internet Gaming Disorder Test. Although Inform cannot diagnose, it is our hope to help people by drawing awareness to areas of concern."
